1 AN ACT
2 To enact R.S. 56:116.7, relative to outlaw quadrupeds; to provide that private property
3 owners do not need a license to take outlaw quadrupeds on their own property; and
4 to provide for related matters.
5 Be it enacted by the Legislature of Louisiana:
6 Section 1. R.S. 56:116.7 is hereby enacted to read as follows:
7 §116.7. Special provisions applicable to outlaw quadrupeds
8 Notwithstanding any provision of law to the contrary, owners of private
9 property shall not be required to obtain a hunting license to take outlaw quadrupeds
10 within the bounds of their own private property.
